# Copy the ghost database to jekyll local repo
Go to oyaji-hiking.saigos.space/admin -> lab and Export ghost json backup file to local vm with jekyll repo
Follow the Usage instructions here - https://github.com/eloyesp/jekyll_ghost_importer

